# Superpowers visual-companion brainstorm artifacts
.superpowers/

# graphify knowledge graph: only the hand-curated paper-to-code bridge edges are
# tracked. The full graph.json and GRAPH_REPORT.md are large, churny, and
# regenerable (`graphify update .`), so they're local-only — as are cache/,
# cost.json, manifest.json, the HTML viz, and the .graphify_* dotfiles.
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/bridge-edges.json
